                <h1>7.VANDHE BHARATH EXPRESS</h1>
                Vande Bharat Express is a recently launched, fully air-conditioned, semi-high-speed, intercity
                day-train. Also known as Train 18, this train offers various facilities, such as CCTV cameras, Wi-Fi,
                hydraulic-pressure doors, snack tables, and smoke/fire detection and extinguishing system. It runs at a
                speed of 200 km/hr, making it one of the fastest trains in India.
                <br>
                <a href="/search"> <input id="pass" type="submit" name="submit" value="BOOK NOW" class="btn btn-lg btn-success"></a>
                <!-- <input type="button" value="BOOK NOW"> -->
            </div>
            <div class="col">
                <img width="100%" src="vandhe.jpg" alt="">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container text-center">
