            </div>
            <div class="col">
                <h1> 8.MOUNTAIN RAILWAYS</h1>


                Mountain Railways are train lines that pass through the mountains of India. Out of the seven mountain
                railways of
                the country, three have been declared as World Heritage Sites by UNESCO and named as Mountain Railways
                of India.
                These are the Darjeeling Himalayan Railway aka Toy Train, the Kalka–Shimla Railway, and the Nilgiri
                Mountain
                Railway.
                <br>
                <a href="/search"><input id="pass" type="submit" name="submit" value="BOOK NOW" class="btn btn-lg btn-success"></a>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container text-center">
